title: Nissan car sales in Europe 2003 to 2018
summary: Overall Number of units sold has increased over the Year.
Number of units sold is roughly constant from 2011 to 2013, and lastly slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Number of units sold, of value 554046.0 was reached at Year 2015
Minimum Number of units sold about 421134.0 was reached at Year 2013
